com.camerontec.catalys.server.ha.collections.message

Class WriteRequestMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.camerontec.catalys.server.ha.collections.message.DistributedCollectionMessage
      • com.camerontec.catalys.server.ha.collections.message.WriteRequestMessage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ExternalizableData, Cloneable

    public final class WriteRequestMessage
extends DistributedCollectionMessage
implements Cloneable
    Class representing a write request message.

    A write request is any request which seeks to modify the state of a distributed object.

    See Also:
